Total: 7 issues (2 CRITICAL, 4 MEDIUM, 1 LOW)

## Additional Risks
- The prompt is very strong on UI replacement boundaries, but it assumes backend/request-type compatibility that is not proven inside the target file.
- Keeping legacy `menu` sync while hiding its UI creates a real risk of “stuck badge but nothing visible to cancel”.
- Because the help drawer block is replaced almost wholesale, any copy-paste truncation around the `showOtherForm` block or closing tags would be hard to spot unless the prompt asks for a post-replacement structural re-read.

